Package: edinetsynth
Title: Forensic Evaluation and Tidy Tools for Synthetic EDINET Datasets
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("ML Upskill Agents UG", email = "workflow.tools@icloud.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Forensic evaluation tools, structural fidelity checks, and
    deterministic anomaly injection for synthetic Japanese securities reports
    (有価証券報告書) generated by the VilseckKI Synth-Factory. Provides tidy
    accessors for segment extraction, flaw taxonomy analysis, quality tier
    comparison with statistical validation, Hugging Face dataset export, and
    publication-quality visualizations for marketplace listings and academic
    papers. Bridges R-based analysis workflows with Python NLP training
    pipelines.
